Dancer-Template-Ctpp2

Allows Dancer applications to use HTML::CTPP2 template engine to render views.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test
        make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Dancer::Template::Ctpp2

You can also look for information at:

    HTTP::CTPP2 module documentation:
        perldoc HTML::CTPP2

    CTPP2 library documentation:
        http://ctpp.havoc.ru/en/index.html - in English
        http://ctpp.havoc.ru/index.html - in Russian

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/HTML-CTPP2/lib/HTML/CTPP2.pm/
        

